{{Top|leg}}
'''Zisians''' were [[Near-Human]]s with scaly green skin and orange eyes. In their old age, they often suffered from rheumy eyes and wrinkled skin hanging in loose flaps. One individual of the race was [[Ganar Tos]].<ref name="The Paradise Snare">''[[The Paradise Snare]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
While the physical description of Ganar Tos seems somewhat reptilian, his voice is described as "human,"<ref name="Rebel Dawn">''[[Rebel Dawn]]''</ref> the term [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] is used in the text rather than Near-Human, and he apparently expected to be able to have children with a [[Human/Legends|Human]] woman, [[Bria Tharen]].<ref name="The Paradise Snare" /> For this to be possible, the Zisian species would have to be closely related to baseline Humans.

